title: iShares Edge MSCI Multifactor Intl (INTF) Shares Cross Above 200 DMA - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Wednesday, shares of the iShares Edge MSCI Multifactor Intl ETF (Symbol: INTF) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $25.64, changing hands as high as $25.65 per share. iShares Edge MSCI Multifactor Intl shares are currently trading up about 0.4% on the day.
